              I had an issue with an LG smart TV that when connected to the network would turn itself off at random intervals. The UI also got incredibly laggy and everything stuttered.<br /><br />The culprit? Some photo software that my room mate installed on his machine that flooded the network with UPnP packets that the TV was trying to respond to.<br /><br />Now THAT was fun to try and diagnose....

              

              
              
