          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              <div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">What's the oddest tech issue you've ever experienced?</div><br /><br />A while ago, I had a programming bug, where the touch screen controls had stopped working because I forgot to take into account the fourth dimension in my translate function. <br /><br />I was using an old matrix library that was optimized for 2D transforms, and it just ignored the w component, so the inverse transform was not calculated with the proper perspective divide.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
