          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              I remember several, but a suddenly missing Volume Control on Win 98 was the oddest.<br /><br /> The &quot;X&quot; and &quot;Y&quot; coordinates that position the volume control window from last opening got trashed in the registry, and went to 3000! (this was around 2000, so it was off the screen for sure).<br /><br /> Fortunately, by changing the X and Y values of HKEY_CURRENT_ USER - VOLUME CONTROL did the trick, but finding out what it actually caused this wasn't easy.<br /><br /> These things happen.<br /><br />Edited for grammar.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
