            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              I work in tech support so have many of these odd stories...the weirdest one has to be the guy whose computer rebooted every time he flushed the toilet!<br /><br />No one believed him but he was phoning every day and was adamant that it was really happening. Eventually we relented and sent an engineer to his house who discovered that he lived in the sticks and had a septic tank with an electric pump to pump the waste into it. The pump was on the same circuit as the socket his computer was plugged into and when it kicked in the current draw was just too high and the computer had its power interrupted! We told him to go get his wiring sorted out and buy a ups in the meantime!

              

              
              
            </div>
